WEBVTT

00:00:01.436 --> 00:00:03.079
Mpendwa Abuelita,

00:00:03.103 --> 00:00:05.357
Najua sijakuwepo nyumbani kwa muda.

00:00:05.381 --> 00:00:07.688
Uko nyumbani kwetu pazuri Mexico,

00:00:07.712 --> 00:00:10.061
nami niko hapa Marekani,

00:00:10.085 --> 00:00:11.458
nikipigania maisha 
yetu ya baadaye.

00:00:11.927 --> 00:00:14.299
Pengine unanyunyuzia ua waridi maji,

00:00:14.323 --> 00:00:16.171
ukitunza fyulisi

00:00:16.195 --> 00:00:18.995
na kuhakikisha kua kasa wako wameshiba.

00:00:19.474 --> 00:00:22.259
Hiyo ni mojawapo ya vitu,
navikumbuka sana kuhusu nyumbani --

00:00:22.283 --> 00:00:24.267
kupoteza muda na maua

00:00:24.291 --> 00:00:26.773
ukinihadithia kuhusu utoto wako

00:00:28.004 --> 00:00:31.988
Unavyojua,
tumeishi New York City tangu 2015